tspan.tspan: extend_leaf(G,L): Algorithm for extending a group G with a leaf L.
- N: a non-leaf node representing an extension of G that includes L.
(LOGICAL DEPENDENCIES:ALGO STEP LABEL) ALGO STEP DESCRIPTION
(a) Insert a non-leaf node. Call the node N.
(a:b) Insert a red edge from N to L.
(a:c) Insert a blue edge from N to G.
- The visualization assumes that immediately after this algorithm completes,
commit_transaction(G,N) is called and succeeds. The result of this call is not
- Each visualization is drawn starting from the pink node.
L may be reachable from G
